| Gaim Renamed &mdash; Now Pidgin IM                                 |
|   from the speak-freely dept.                                      |
|   posted by kdawson on Saturday April 07, @21:26 (Software)        |
|   http://linux.slashdot.org/article.pl?sid=07/04/07/2014230        |
+--------------------------------------------------------------------+

An anonymous reader writes "Announced on the Gaim mailing lists earlier
today, [0]the Gaim project is being renamed. This follows a lengthy and,
unfortunately, secret legal process with AOL, which also prevented any
code releases except betas. The project will now be known as [1]Pidgin IM.
Development is being migrated off of sourceforge.net as well and is now
being hosted on [2]developer.pidgin.im"

Discuss this story at:
    http://linux.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=07/04/07/2014230

